# Welcome to the portfolio of Jeffrey Miller
You have come to Jeffrey Miller's portfolio. Here you may find links to some of my projects.
Currently, there is only one project I can share.

## Visit my Github page
You can find all of my work here @Grexel.

## Download my programs
Dowload my programs here: [HostedPrograms](http://csmupa.com/~millerjl07/pub1000/hostedPrograms/)
I coded one quick program to share for this website (10/28/2016) which is called LSystemTrees.
It creates a random dictionary of rules and will draw the LSystem with a user given amount of iterations.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
